metadata.name: E'ART'H _ 01
metadata.description:
E'ART'H _ 01

Genesise drop

- The universe is born at every moment of inhale and exhale.
Everything is connected and affects each other.  
< Digital cyanotype, motion graphic loop media, 6", Tongue drum >

1stride is the “Inner-Art-Messenger” that visualizes resonating messages from deep inside her heart and makes them into motion graphics.
Mainly explores the connection value of center, balance, and resonance.

Inspired by a physical cynotype print using light + shadow + water, the E'ART'H collection was born.
